token_lists.title: Edinburgh
token_lists.description: "...To work around the Symbiotics, the Sentinels started moving small groups of humans through the portals into Elfame. One such portal was hidden in Mary King’s Close, under the Royal Mile in Edinburgh. The Close had a reputation since the 17th century for hauntings and murders. Mysterious lights appeared. This tended to keep people away. The Close was the perfect place to hide a portal." Read more - https://medium.com/@wicgan/portal-to-elfame-c5e738201938
